e Questions for SSC CGL Tier 2"}]},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/#website","url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/","name":"Oliveboard","description":"Free Govt. Exam Alerts &amp; Resources","publisher":{"@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/#organization"},"potentialAction":[{"@type":"SearchAction","target":{"@type":"EntryPoint","urlTemplate":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/?s={search_term_string}"},"query-input":{"@type":"PropertyValueSpecification","valueRequired":true,"valueName":"search_term_string"}}],"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/#organization","name":"Oliveboard","url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/#/schema/logo/image/","url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/logo.png","contentUrl":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/logo.png","width":150,"height":40,"caption":"Oliveboard"},"image":{"@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/#/schema/logo/image/"},"sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/Oliveboard","https://x.com/Oliveboard","https://www.instagram.com/oliveboard.in/","https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRvrHAyNdOMI_JBkE2pjZtw?sub_confirmation=1"]},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/#/schema/person/2f25f4d24adbf225bc11e6a0a4bcad8b","name":"Mahima Khurana","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/#/schema/person/image/","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/922450c81513b569654b520958cbf86230a614fd2f7f05d6b46674fe4bce8c99?s=96&d=mm&r=g","contentUrl":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/922450c81513b569654b520958cbf86230a614fd2f7f05d6b46674fe4bce8c99?s=96&d=mm&r=g","caption":"Mahima Khurana"},"description":"I’m Mahima Khurana, a writer with a strong passion for creating meaningful, learner-focused content especially in the field of competitive exam preparation. From authoring books and developing thousands of practice questions to crafting articles and study material, I specialize in transforming complex exam-related topics into clear, engaging, and accessible content. I have first hand experience of 5+ months in SSC Exams. Writing, for me, is not just a skill but a way to support and guide aspirants through their preparation journey one well-written explanation at a time."},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148077281","position":1,"url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148077281","name":"Q1. What are the most repeated topics in SSC CGL Quantitative Aptitude?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ans. Arithmetic topics like Time &amp; Work, Time, Speed &amp; Distance, Percentage, Profit &amp; Loss, Simple &amp; Compound Interest, Ratio &amp; Proportion, Mixture &amp; Alligation, Averages, and Number System &amp; HCF/LCM are frequently asked. Advanced Mathematics topics like Algebra, Geometry, Mensuration, Trigonometry, and Data Interpretation also appear regularly.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148090949","position":2,"url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148090949","name":"Q2. How difficult are SSC CGL Quantitative Aptitude questions in Tier 2?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ans. Tier 2 questions are generally high difficulty. They test not just formulas but also problem-solving speed, logical reasoning, and application of concepts in slightly complex scenarios.<br/>","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148095470","position":3,"url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148095470","name":"Q3. Are there shortcut methods to solve these questions quickly?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ans. Yes. Shortcut formulas for simple vs. compound interest, percentages, ratio calculations, HCF/LCM, and cyclicity can save valuable time in the exam.<br/>","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148099966","position":4,"url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148099966","name":"Q4. How should I prepare for repeated questions?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ans. Focus on mastering the high-frequency topics listed above, practice previous years’ questions, and revise formulas regularly. Daily practice of SSC CGL quant practice questions improves speed and accuracy.<br/>","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148104632","position":5,"url":"https://www.oliveboard.in/blog/most-repeated-quantitative-aptitude-questions-for-ssc-cgl-tier-2/#faq-question-1759148104632","name":"Q5. Do I need to only memorize formulas to score well?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ans. No. Understanding the underlying concepts is important. Memorization alone may not help in solving questions with slight twists or higher difficulty.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"}]}</script>
